c=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ny-daily-news-masks-hospitals.jpg?resize=800%2C474&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"Screenshot of NY Daily News with a headline that reads &quot;As Covid Spikes in NYC, Mask Mandates Return to City Hospitals.&quot; The article includes an image of a sign in a window with a headline that reads &quot;Wear your mask even if you're vaxxed&quot; with a person in the background wearing a mask.\" class=\"wp-image-12997\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ny-daily-news-masks-hospitals.jpg?w=2172&amp;ssl=1 2172w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ny-daily-news-masks-hospitals.jpg?resize=768%2C454&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ny-daily-news-masks-hospitals.jpg?w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>A 1\/3\/24 article in the New York Daily News has the headline <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.nydailynews.com\/2024\/01\/03\/as-covid-spikes-in-nyc-mask-mandates-return-to-city-hospitals\/\" target=\"_blank\">&#8220;As Covid Spikes in NYC, Mask Mandates Return to City Hospitals&#8221;<\/a>, which notes:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>With COVID, flu, and RSV on the rise the NYC public hospital system brought back masking requirements just after Christmas 2023. The spike in this &#8220;tripledemic&#8221; predicted by the CDC in September 2023 continues to put disabled and especially immuno-compromised people at increased risk.<br><br>This December 2023 data from the CDC shows New York City reached the \u201cvery high\u201d level of respiratory illness, the highest level on the CDC\u2019s scale.<br><br>Possibility contributing to the spike is the fact that while over 80% of New Yorkers have received their first COVID vaccine, just 18% of the total population has received the bivalent booster.<\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2014 Faye Ginsburg<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A 1\/3\/24 article in the New York Daily News has the headline &#8220;As Covid Spikes in NYC, Mask Mandates Return to City Hospitals&#8221;, which notes: With COVID, flu, and RSV on the rise the NYC public hospital system brought back masking requirements just after Christmas 2023. The spike in this&hellip; <a class=\"continue\" href=\"https:\/\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/as-covid-spikes-in-city-hospitals-mask-mandates-return-january-3-2024\/\">Continue Reading<span> As COVID Spikes in City Hospitals, Mask Mandates Return (January 3, 2024)<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":12997,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"advanced_seo_description":"","jetpack_seo_html_title":"","jetpack_seo_noindex":false,"_FSMCFIC_featured_image_caption":"","_FSMCFIC_featured_image_nocaption":"","_FSMCFIC_featured_image_hide":""},"categories":[44],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ny-daily-news-masks-hospitals.jpg?fit=2172%2C1286&ssl=1","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/12988"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=12988"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/disabilitycovidchronicles.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/12988\/re